      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the info. i'm just worried about the cost of another doctor visit and the hassle. i read online that sometimes you just need to drink more water to help your body process it better. would increasing my water intake a lot help with the nausea and the shakes?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
