      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, if i drink too much water it makes it worse? i thought the opposite because i heard lithium makes you pee more. i'm also feeling a little dizzy today too. honestly i'm just really exhausted and i feel like i can't keep up with work. if i just take a slightly lower dose for a few days to see if the shaking stops, that would be okay right? it seems safer than waiting for a doctor appointment.",
